619
00:31:33,079 --> 00:31:34,279
Those were your rules,

620
00:31:34,279 --> 00:31:34,839
Elder Yu.

621
00:31:36,240 --> 00:31:36,759
Go!

622
00:31:43,390 --> 00:31:44,930
White Chess No. 2 will take three steps.

623
00:31:50,079 --> 00:31:51,799
Black Chess No. 4 will take four steps.

624
00:31:52,200 --> 00:31:53,400
How exciting.

625
00:31:53,400 --> 00:31:54,240
