727
00:37:33,280 --> 00:37:34,199
I'm sorry,

728
00:37:34,199 --> 00:37:34,800
Zhuoran.

729
00:37:35,159 --> 00:37:36,000
I'm sorry.

730
00:37:36,440 --> 00:37:38,320
